    "en": {
      "title": "Cope - Nalin talks about the reason why Cope is holding back",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Nalin Bandara, the Kurunegala District Councilor of the Samagi Jana Balavega, said that the formation of COP and COPA committees is being pushed back because the party has to give its chairman positions.",
        "Cope and Cope Committees have not yet been formed. Why are these being pulled back? Is this trying to destroy the opportunity to give the chairmanship of these committees to the opposition?",
        "It has been agreed to announce the COP and COPA committees as soon as the speaker returns from abroad. He is scheduled to arrive in the island today."
      ],
